<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>You've been invited to {{projectName}}</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background: #1a1a2e; padding: 32px 40px; }
    .header h1 { color: #fff; margin: 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; }
    .body { padding: 32px 40px; color: #333; }
    .body p { line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .role-badge { display: inline-block; background: #e8f0fe; color: #1a73e8; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; }
    .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: #1a73e8; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0; }
    .install-section { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px 24px; margin: 24px 0; }
    .install-section h3 { margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 15px; color: #444; }
    .code { font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; background: #1a1a2e; color: #e2e8f0; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 13px; display: block; margin: 6px 0; overflow-x: auto; }
    .footer { padding: 20px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; color: #888; font-size: 12px; }
    .footer a { color: #1a73e8; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>emergent memory</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Hi there,</p>
      <p>
        <strong>{{inviterName}}</strong> has invited you to join the project
        <strong>{{projectName}}</strong> as a <span class="role-badge">{{roleLabel}}</span>.
      </p>

      <a href="{{acceptUrl}}" class="cta-button">Accept invitation</a>

      <p>This invitation expires in <strong>7 days</strong>.</p>

      <div class="install-section">
        <h3>New to emergent memory? Get started in 3 steps:</h3>
        <p><strong>1. Install the CLI</strong></p>
        <span class="code">curl -fsSL https://get.emergent.memory/install.sh | sh</span>
        <p style="margin-top:14px"><strong>2. Log in</strong></p>
        <span class="code">memory login</span>
        <p style="margin-top:14px"><strong>3. After accepting, connect to the project</strong></p>
        <span class="code">memory projects set {{projectName}}</span>
      </div>

      <p>
        Or accept directly in the browser using the button above.
      </p>

      <p>If you weren't expecting this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

      <p>— The emergent memory team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        Invitation link: <a href="{{acceptUrl}}">{{acceptUrl}}</a><br>
        Sent from emergent memory · <a href="https://emergent.memory">emergent.memory</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
